# BYD Car Sales Dashboard

This project is a dashboard for BYD car sales data, featuring both a frontend visualization system and an admin backend for data management.

## Project Structure

- [index.html](mdc:index.html): Main frontend dashboard that displays BYD car sales data
- [css/style.css](mdc:css/style.css): Styling for the frontend dashboard
- [js/main.js](mdc:js/main.js): Frontend JavaScript functionality
- [admin/app.py](mdc:admin/app.py): Flask admin backend application
- [admin/requirements.txt](mdc:admin/requirements.txt): Python dependencies for the admin system
- [admin/README.md](mdc:admin/README.md): Documentation for the admin system

## Frontend

The frontend is a responsive dashboard showcasing BYD car sales data with interactive charts and data visualization. It uses:

- HTML/CSS/JavaScript
- ECharts for data visualization
- Particles.js for visual effects

## Admin Backend

The admin backend is a Flask application that:

- Manages car sales data
- Provides user authentication and authorization
- Has role-based access control (admin, editor, viewer)
- Stores data in JSON files
